## PROHIBITED Architectural Patterns

❌ **Direct Component Communication**: Must communicate through orchestrator
❌ **Bypassing Registration**: All components must register with orchestrator
❌ **Independent Trading**: All trades require RiskManager authorization (Rule 4)
❌ **Skipping Regime Context**: Cannot process signals without regime awareness
❌ **Direct Database Access**: Must use ClickHouseDataManager (Rule 3)
❌ **Strategy Isolation**: Strategies must coordinate through StrategyManager (Rule 5)
❌ **Unmanaged Lifecycle**: All components must implement ISystemComponent

